narrativeSections.additionalInfo: You are the assigned Combat Medic for Alpha Squad conducting a key leader engagement with local governance in Sector 9 of the city. Your team has completed its primary objective of establishing relations with the district representative in the municipal building. Upon exfiltration at approximately 1430 hours, your squad encounters a civilian demonstration blocking the planned extraction route. While establishing an alternate evacuation corridor, a significant explosion occurs at grid coordinates Bravo-3, followed by small arms fire from multiple points of origin. Multiple casualties have been reported, including both US personnel and local nationals. The security situation remains fluid with unconfirmed reports of armed combatants in the vicinity..
